headline: IonQ Stock Is Tumbling. A Director Just Made a Big Buy of Shares.
summary: IonQ  stock has dropped precipitously so far this year, and one director just bought a large block of shares of the quantum-computing company.  IonQ is coming off a hot year.  Just a few days into 2025, however,  Nvidia  CEO Jensen Huang said that quantum computing wouldn’t be useful for decades.
